  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Codec
    Encoder/Decoder for Cell.
    Codec.Decoder
    Implementations should implicitly clean up any resources allocated when the Decoder/CellScanner runs off the end of the cell block.
    Codec.Encoder
    Call flush when done.
